<Class name="CMIF_RailCars" id="24843570-1784-4275-94ec-e14a48d7a933">
    <superclass name="CMIF_OpsViewTables"/>
    <transient/>
    <persistentAllowed/>
    <sharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassPersistentAllowed/>
    <subclassSharedTransientAllowed/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>


This is a WAGON, and for each WAGON visit there is a rail car visit in N4 these are seperate.
In MTN we will have to send rail_car, rail_car_platforms and rail_car_visit for each wagon.

DATASET - Rail

Mapping 
 MTN : 
 N4  : rail_cars
 
[gkey]							[bigint]			NOT NULL,
[id]							[nvarchar](255)		NOT NULL,
[rr_gkey]						[bigint]			NOT NULL,
[tare_weight_kg]				[float64]			NOT NULL,
[safe_weight_kg]				[float64]			NOT NULL,
[max_tiers_per_platform]		[bigint]			NOT NULL,
[max_20s_per_platform]			[bigint]			NOT NULL,
[length_cm]						[float64]			NULL,
[floor_height_cm]				[float64]			NULL,
[flat_car_type]					[nvarchar](255)		NULL,


</text>
